    Interface Description
    IAgeCalculator
    The Age Calculator has only three functions.
    ICalendar
    A calendar has only one possible action: buildCalendar, which allows to show the calendar given by the month and year the user inputs.
    IChronometer
    This interface sets the core functionality of a simple chronometer.
    IDateCalculator
    The Date Calculator is responsible for all the operations based on LocalDate.
    INotebook
    The Notebook is responsible for handling appointments.
    ITimeCalculator  
    ITravels
    The Travel interface is responsible for all functions related to traveling queries.
